These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
House: ranch-style, townhouse, futuristic, cottage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, orchid, poppy
City: hamburg, colone, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
3. the cottage house is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the ranch-style house is the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| House    | townhouse  | cottage | futuristic    | ranch-style       |
| Flower         | rose | poppy    | orchid      | dahlia |
| City   | hamburg   | san-francisco | colone | edinburgh        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, tea, fanta
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, singing, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, fantasy, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person watching action movies is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Beverage        | tea   | juice | water     | fanta      |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing | writing | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | action   | fantasy     | musical      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, ship, car
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, sports, martial-arts, time-travel
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, software-developer, scientist, doctor
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the doctor is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the doctor is on the right of the scientist##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Transport         | jet-ski | helicopter | ship | car |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel       | sports    | family | martial-arts     |
| Job   | chef | scientist    | doctor | software-developer    |

