.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
House: victorian, art-deco, colonial, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, photography, puzzles, cooking
City: venice, edinburgh, colone, liverpool
1. the colonial house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the colonial house##1
7. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| House         | victorian | gothic-revival | colonial | art-deco |
| Hobby       | photography     | cooking      | reading     | puzzles      |
| City   | edinburgh | venice         | liverpool      | colone        |

