.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, mirinda, cola
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, april, november
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, mexican, polish
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the canadian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the dutch##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person drinking cola is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage         | mirinda   | cola | lemonade  | 7up      |
| Birthday   | april  | december        | november  | july       |
| Nationality         | canadian | mexican    | dutch | polish |

