.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: domino, monopoly, whist, bridge
City: hannover, san-francisco, miami, rome
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, balloon-flower, azalea
1. the person playing domino is the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to miami is the person playing whist##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person playing bridge is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game           | monopoly | whist | bridge | domino |
| City   | rome   | miami  | san-francisco | hannover   |
| Flower   | azalea   | sunflower     | balloon-flower | aconite       |

