.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, domino, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, ambient, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, tram, quad-bike
1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person playing domino##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
8. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Game          | monopoly  | mah-jongg | domino   | backgammon     |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | hip-hop   | gospel  | ambient |
| Transport   | tram         | bike  | roller | quad-bike  |

