.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, radish, lime, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, chess, skydiving, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, car, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the person eating radish is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating lime##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person eating radish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food      | peach | lime     | cucumber | radish |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | gardening | skydiving       | chess    |
| Transport   | car   | jet-ski | taxi    | motorbike |

