.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, librarian, analyst
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, iris, daisy
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, yellow, purple, fuchsia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the analyst##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person who likes purple is the dancer##1
5. the dancer is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job          | librarian        | analyst   | dancer  | lawyer   |
| Flower   | lily         | daisy     | zinnia    | iris       |
| Color         | yellow | white | purple | fuchsia |

