4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, go
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, thai, french, british
1. the fan of folk is the british##1
2. the thai is on the left of the french##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the fan of metal is on the right of the british##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
6. the fan of rock is on the left of the british##1
7. the person playing chess is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | rock | folk | metal        |
| Game       | go | chess  | snooker | monopoly     |
| Nationality        | thai    | french   | british  | dutch |

