.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, cat, horse, fish
House: cape-cod, cottage, art-deco, futuristic
City: colone, nizza, hamburg, liverpool
1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
7. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the art-deco house is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Pet         | pony  | fish | cat  | horse |
| House       | art-deco | cottage        | futuristic | cape-cod       |
| City   | colone   | nizza          | liverpool          | hamburg       |

