.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, garlic, grapes, cucumber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cycling, handball, weightlifting
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, mouse, turtle
1. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating garlic##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
6. the person eating pepper is the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food         | cucumber   | grapes   | pepper | garlic |
| Sport   | handball | surfing | cycling   | weightlifting |
| Pet   | turtle     | horse  | mouse  | fish  |

