There 4 different types of food: pear, apple, peas, lettuce
House: townhouse, modern, cape-cod, wooden
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the cape-cod house is the person eating lettuce##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating pear##1
7. the townhouse house is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Game         | canasta | snooker    | scrabble        | backgammon |
| Food   | apple     | peas     | lettuce        | pear   |
| House         | modern   | townhouse | cape-cod | wooden  |

