There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, brown, yellow, orange
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, azalea, orchid
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the cottage house is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| House   | palace   | cape-cod  | gothic-revival    | cottage    |
| Color   | orange | yellow  | aquamarine  | brown |
