.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, baccarat, oliveros, bongani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, funk, r&b
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, traveling, sudoku, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of r&b is the bongani-smoker##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
7. the swisher-smoker is the fan of electronic##1
8. the fan of funk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar      | swisher        | bongani    | baccarat | oliveros      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic        | r&b   | hip-hop  | funk  |
| Hobby         | dancing | traveling | sudoku   | photography |

