There are 4 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, lilac, fuchsia
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar           | bolivar  | chaman | aristoff  | fonseca |
| Birthday   | february    | june       | march | november      |
| Color   | chestnut | white  | fuchsia    | lilac    |

