.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
House: art-deco, modern, farmhouse, tower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, tea, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, woodworking, photography, traveling
1. the modern house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
7. the tower house is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| House           | modern  | farmhouse  | art-deco | tower |
| Beverage   | sprite   | lemonade | almond-milk   | tea      |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography    | woodworking   | traveling         |

 